"of :c:type:`NPY_CLIPMODE` values. The number of clipmodes *n* must be known "
"before calling this function. This function is provided to help functions "
"allow a different clipmode for each dimension."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/c-api/array.rst:3080
