#: ../../../reference/c-api/array.rst:3088
msgid "#define error_converting(x) (((x) == -1) && PyErr_Occurred())"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/c-api/array.rst:3094
msgid ""
"Convert all kinds of Python objects (including arrays and array scalars) to "
"a (platform-pointer-sized) integer. On error, -1 is returned and an "
"exception set."
