#: ../../../reference/c-api/array.rst:3101
msgid ""
"Convert any Python sequence (or single Python number) passed in as *seq* to "
"(up to) *maxvals* pointer-sized integers and place them in the *vals* array. "
"The sequence can be smaller then *maxvals* as the number of converted "
